            <title>[LU-8550] problems of conf-sanity test_32  </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8550</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1) test_32a: The MGS should be umounted otherwise the seperate MGS will cause failure of conf-sanity 32a. and re-start mgs in t32_test_cleanup() because mgs need be always started. &lt;br/&gt;
2) test_32c: Format and tunefs on the same mds in conf-sanity 32 tests If mds1 and mds2 are different machine, conf-sanity 32c will fail.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
